{"tid":2449523,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒 經典歌（","createTime":"2021-03-16T17:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T14:37:13.000Z","uid":108756,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"40706f545950349ff664e86b4b18a226edf1b936","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"01/02年既玉蝴蝶live<br />\n老實講唱得最好係呢兩次 打後05年同10年代再出黎唱都差好遠<br />\n雖然佢今日賺盡人仔 又變哂大陸仔 同啲大陸仔唱歌<br />\n但我覺得當年既佢其實值得今日既後生仔知道佢曾經係個歌手 而唔係演員 唔係出黎煮野食既人（唔用廚師 因為自己係佢fans都講唔出佢係一個廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S7tKMJPiCdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS7tKMJPiCdY&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=fa97358b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S7tKMJPiCdY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XFe_Iyf7I4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXFe_Iyf7I4k&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=2ab76dbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XFe_Iyf7I4k</a><br />\n同埋佢好似有好多live都無人發覺/睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冥想 live 呢首都好少人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m4_1eUydSv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm4_1eUydSv4&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=bda4510d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m4_1eUydSv4</a><br />\n末世紀的呼聲 呢首viva live好型<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UZgS4I3RCq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUZgS4I3RCq0&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6d2ad9aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UZgS4I3RCq0</a><br />\n罪人 viva live<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mGfhA6JXrcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmGfhA6JXrcs&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=644da6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mGfhA6JXrcs</a><br />\n<br />\n國語歌 又點止一首因為愛所以愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠了沒有 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nqTFaOpTp1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnqTFaOpTp1c&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=65b40b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nqTFaOpTp1c</a><br />\n281公里 （呢首live收音差 一係就近幾年先再唱live但已經唔係個回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nG_c_Ap1jsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnG_c_Ap1jsk&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=5c852fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nG_c_Ap1jsk</a><br />\n你不會了解 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iSp_byES0C0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiSp_byES0C0&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=f408b9f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iSp_byES0C0</a>"},{"pid":"a681b8e37603a123ba2794a84255179d4d86e68b","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"經典情歌 非走不可<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lG3Du_Cqv_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlG3Du_Cqv_Q&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=94d9d298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lG3Du_Cqv_Q</a><br />\n就算上勁歌都好穩定<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kYynehk8okE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkYynehk8okE&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=f821b887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kYynehk8okE</a><br />\n<br />\n無聲彷有聲（講真我覺得呢首其實算高音同難keep住成首唱得好）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fYL54JW1IPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfYL54JW1IPc&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjr