e":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"彈開/曝光<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YQRBmTOVJeY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYQRBmTOVJeY&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=5b2ab0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YQRBmTOVJeY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GeOMLEaeNQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGeOMLEaeNQY&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=a37df7bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GeOMLEaeNQY</a><br />\n我覺得彈開好聽過曝光 但唔知點解當年會推曝光"},{"pid":"27969ae16827ed4ce5fca0adb4a78c8a9e6f17f1","tid":2449523,"uid":205684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491e5525d52d31e4da1282e2e7146ea27957a028","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"經典搖滾 （唔好屌佢唔識彈結他住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹聽歌算啦）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wPl6ROejI4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwPl6ROejI4o&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=130c45a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wPl6ROejI4o</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sMiOolRBMyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsMiOolRBMyA&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=3016d2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sMiOolRBMyA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S0yB8ER8yEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS0yB8ER8yEA&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6326c2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S0yB8ER8yEA</a><br />\n唔明點解又係唱到差咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d06ba87e2c045bb68c4625a182324ecdaf4f20a","tid":2449523,"uid":384040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"你的天空宇宙只夠我流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不可跳舞<br />\n<br />\n今天開始哪個都不愛 抱你抱到通訊社轉載<br />\n兩極變成赤道仍沒法分開<br />\n<br />\n最寬廣的公園遊樂過 為何認真 若我尚佔一席位 <br />\n都想入座 觀賞這個驚險人生<br />\n<br />\n和情人深深一吻來代替講話好嗎~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假使當初可以為了你　忘了愛所有人 <br />\n分開手去追尋　足可擁抱千萬人 <br />\n即使天空海闊沒有愛　還有你這個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生讀書時期失戀真係聽到流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188e756783834eaee6b36b5826da4942ebb234a4","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27969ae16827ed4ce5fca0adb4a78c8a9e6f17f1","tid":2449523,"uid":205684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"識野 但我怕會有人講李榮浩唱得好聽過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X8hGyQ89hRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX8hGyQ89hRs&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=e18b3bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X8hGyQ89hRs</a> 其實live唔差 <br />\n不過我睇佢今時今日似唔敢再唱live <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a8de61539a088e3180c5b017d9eafe7bfbd2cd","tid":2449523,"uid":346722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc