gmoji\" /><br />\n夠了沒有 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nqTFaOpTp1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnqTFaOpTp1c&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=65b40b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nqTFaOpTp1c</a><br />\n281公里 （呢首live收音差 一係就近幾年先再唱live但已經唔係個回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nG_c_Ap1jsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnG_c_Ap1jsk&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=5c852fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nG_c_Ap1jsk</a><br />\n你不會了解 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iSp_byES0C0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiSp_byES0C0&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=f408b9f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iSp_byES0C0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"冥想真係好鬼正<br />\n最鍾意愛後餘生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d225da4a252a81911171f7637f06675844ce70a","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"我知好多連登仔會屌鳩佢 <br />\n亦好多人唔鍾意佢<br />\n但只係覺得其實佢歌手時期有好多歌都係被忽略之餘<br />\n好似啲人講親佢都係黎黎去去三數隻<br />\n其實佢係有好多歌可以一聽"},{"pid":"6cb16d62c48d251f112bfe3837bcdd21edd36803","tid":2449523,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"絕大部份都一定會講既活著viva <br />\n攞出黎其實我係想知到底點解佢今時今日唱得差咁多 真心覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（單線solo無謂再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n以前<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MR5tE6FhFAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMR5tE6FhFAU&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHI